{"meta":{"title":"1 Nefi 6","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/6?lang=spa","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ/2017-11-0060-1-nephi-06-64k-spa.mp3?download=true","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"b26621199b8200fcbc37f15773921d70ebd4e5bf","data-aid":"124161716","data-aid-version":"3","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/6","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"spa","data-orig-id":"34085354c9883ef35ff0623e36634ee00725eca2","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"1 Nefi 6","description":"Nefi escribe acerca de las cosas de Dios — El propósito de Nefi es persuadir a los hombres a venir al Dios de Abraham y ser salvos. Aproximadamente 600–592 a.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"1 Nefi 6","description":"Nefi escribe acerca de las cosas de Dios — El propósito de Nefi es persuadir a los hombres a venir al Dios de Abraham y ser salvos. Aproximadamente 600–592 a.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124162194\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 6</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124162195\" id=\"study_summary1\">Nefi escribe acerca de las cosas de Dios — El propósito de Nefi es persuadir a los hombres a venir al Dios de Abraham y ser salvos. Aproximadamente 600–592 a.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124162196\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>Ahora bien, yo, Nefi, no doy la genealogía de mis padres en <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>esta</a> parte de mis anales; ni tampoco la daré en ningún otro momento sobre estas <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>planchas</a> que estoy escribiendo, porque se halla en los anales que mi <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>padre</a> ha llevado, y por eso no la escribo en esta obra.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124162197\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>Básteme decir que somos descendientes de <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>José</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124162198\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Y no me parece importante ocuparme en una narración completa de todas las cosas de mi padre, porque no se pueden escribir sobre <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>estas planchas</a>, pues deseo el espacio para escribir acerca de las cosas de Dios.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124162199\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span>Porque toda mi intención es <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>persuadir</a> a los hombres a que <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>vengan</a> al Dios de Abraham, y al Dios de Isaac, y al Dios de Jacob, y sean salvos.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124161760\" id=\"p5\"><span class=\"verse-number\">5 </span>De modo que no escribo las cosas que <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note5a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>agradan</a> al mundo, sino las que agradan a Dios y a los que no son del mundo.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124161762\" id=\"p6\"><span class=\"verse-number\">6 </span>Por tanto, daré un mandamiento a mis descendientes de que no ocupen estas planchas con cosas que no sean de valor para los hijos de los hombres.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124161764\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.14-15?lang=spa#p14\">2 Ne. 4:14–15</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note1b\" data-full-marker=\"1b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124161765\" id=\"note1b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.2?lang=spa#p2\">1 Ne. 9:2</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note1c\" data-full-marker=\"1c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124161767\" id=\"note1c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.16-17?lang=spa#p16\">1 Ne. 1:16–17</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/19.1-6?lang=spa#p1\">19:1–6</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124161770\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/5.14-16?lang=spa#p14\">1 Ne. 5:14–16</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124161772\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/7.27?lang=spa#p27\">Jacob 7:27</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jarom/1.2,14?lang=spa#p2\">Jarom 1:2, 14</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/omni/1.30?lang=spa#p30\">Omni 1:30</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note4a\" data-full-marker=\"4a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124161775\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/john/20.30-31?lang=spa#p30\">Juan 20:30–31</a>. Véase la <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/bofm-title?lang=spa\">portada del Libro de Mormón</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note4b\" data-full-marker=\"4b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124161777\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.41,45,51?lang=spa#p41\">2 Ne. 9:41, 45, 51</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"5\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note5a\" data-full-marker=\"5a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124161779\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.4?lang=spa#p4\">1 Tes. 2:4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/w-of-m/1.4?lang=spa#p4\">P. de Morm. 1:4</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1a","pid":"124162196","context":"esta","text":"<p data-aid=\"124161764\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.14-15?lang=spa#p14\">2 Ne. 4:14–15</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.14-15?lang=spa#p14","text":"2 Ne. 4:14–15"}]},"note1b":{"id":"note1b","marker":"1b","pid":"124162196","context":"planchas","text":"<p data-aid=\"124161765\" id=\"note1b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.2?lang=spa#p2\">1 Ne. 9:2</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/9.2?lang=spa#p2","text":"1 Ne. 9:2"}]},"note1c":{"id":"note1c","marker":"1c","pid":"124162196","context":"padre","text":"<p data-aid=\"124161767\" id=\"note1c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.16-17?lang=spa#p16\">1 Ne. 1:16–17</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/19.1-6?lang=spa#p1\">19:1–6</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/1.16-17?lang=spa#p16","text":"1 Ne. 1:16–17"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/19.1-6?lang=spa#p1","text":"19:1–6"}]},"note2a":{"id":"note2a","marker":"2a","pid":"124162197","context":"José","text":"<p data-aid=\"124161770\" id=\"note